Title: Cut Off the Head
Description:
Jadzigeth, one of Raszageth's foul lieutenants, proudly leads the Primalists here.

Let us show them all what happens to those who stand against us.
ObjectivesText: Defeat Jadzigeth in the Frostflash Enclave.
PortraitGiverText: Raszageth's lieutenant will be a torrent of trouble until she is stopped.
